==Included files==
[gfx] - directory containing clock images
   gnomeclock by Henrik Hellerstedt <henrik@katedral.se>
   gDesklets clock by Johannes Rebhan <waldgeist@gnome-de.org>
   default and raf by Tuomas Kuosmanen <tigert@ximian.com>
    - rafclock represents the RAF (Royal Air Force) wartime briefing room clock for pilots as far as I know, a nice colorful clock face ;-)
   pocket-watch by GrandMasta
   osX-clock by Pablo
   chrome, dull, fx, modern, and station clock faces were taken from KClock karamba widget (author linuxbob) - GPL license
   rome clock face is from ClockThemed karamba widget (author Sacus) - GPL license
   moon clock face is from DashClock karamba widget (author egon1984) - GPL license
   aero clock face is from Aero-G for Kclock karamba widget (author mirdakas01) - GPL license
   tux and fxtux clock faces by Robert Pastierovic
   [icons] - directory containing icon images for the prefs menu
clock.display - mainsource file
timezones.script - timezone information
README - this file

==Changelog==
ver. 0.55 (Bjoern Koch) 12-11-2011
 - uses new ITime Control 'strftime' attribute to format the date (needs gDesklets 0.36.4+)
ver. 0.54 (Bjoern Koch) 22-01-2011
 - updated Metadata
ver. 0.53 (Bjoern Koch) 20-06-2010
 - fixed Control import error
 - added icons to the prefs menu
ver. 0.52 (Robert Pastierovic)
 - added clock hands styles
ver. 0.51 (Robert Pastierovic)
 - added more clock faces
 - added possibility to change color of clock hands
ver. 0.50.2 (Robert Pastierovic)
 - added disabling some menu entries according to if the date or timezone is displayed 
until ver. 0.50.1 (Martin Grimme)

